<!---->  </span><span class=""> security flaw that exposed millions of candidates' personal information, acquisitions from </span><span class="">
<!---->      <a href="https://ca.linkedin.com/company/workleaphq?trk=article-ssr-frontend-pulse_little-mention" target="_blank" data-tracking-control-name="article-ssr-frontend-pulse_little-mention" data-tracking-will-navigate="" data-test-link="">Workleap<!----></a>
<!---->  </span><span class=""> and </span><span class="">
