<!---->  </span><span class="italic">.</span><span class=""> His mission? To siphon precious Slack intel, feeding secrets back to eager executives. But when his cover is blown, the hunter becomes the hunted. Trapped in a bathroom in Dublin, heart pounding, he watches the door—will he escape unseen, or is this the end of the line? As investigators close in, one question remains: </span><span class="italic font-[700]">Does this conspiracy reach all the way to the top of the Deel C-Suite?!</span><!---->
