<!---->  </span><span class="">. The move aims to integrate Seasoned's AI-driven tech, real-time hiring insights and recruiting automation. Full press release </span><span class=""><a href="https://www.jobget.com/press/releases/jobget-acquires-seasoned-leads-ai-driven-hourly-hiring" target="_blank" data-tracking-control-name="article-ssr-frontend-pulse_little-text-block" data-tracking-will-navigate="" data-test-link="">here<!----></a></span><span class="">. </span><!---->
