    tag: 'Automation',
    excerpt: "It was Father’s Day, and I was riding high. I finally snuck out for a round of golf with the buddies (outside my weekly old-man league), and then spent the day enjoying family time. Life was good. Until my phone buzzed: The Red Sox have traded Rafael",
