    tag: 'AI & Future of Work',
    excerpt: "I was reading Lance Haun 's post this week about Klarna 's AI “oopsie” (remember that one from last week’s Wrap?) and it got me thinking: how long until companies start charging us extra just to speak to a real, live human?",
