<!---->  </span><span class=""> to their arsenal of products this week. I'll be interested to see how they roll it out throughout the various ATS systems in their collection (Jobvite, Lever, JazzHR). We all know how bad both candidates hiring teams can be at getting the answers they need in the interviewing process. I remember a couple of past interviews where the hiring manager clearly didn't look at my resume and was wasting both of our time. This should help their customers get their hiring teams to get the right information and make better decisions. More from CEO </span><span class="">
